0:00:00.000,0:00:02.200
Emanueri! (Mwari nesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:00:02.200,0:00:04.200
Rumbidzai Mwari!

0:00:04.200,0:00:06.960
Uchapupu hwangu ndeuhu:

0:00:06.960,0:00:09.340
Zita rangu ndi Mata Williams.

0:00:09.340,0:00:11.480
Ndine makore 54.

0:00:11.480,0:00:14.180
Ini ndiri amai wevana vatanhatu.

0:00:14.180,0:00:17.160
Ini ndinobva ku Bradford, UK.

0:00:17.160,0:00:23.080
Ndakanga ndiri kuenda ku Glasgow ndichibva ku Bradford kunonzwa mwanasikana wangu mukonzati.

0:00:23.080,0:00:25.480
Maawa mashanu nechitima.

0:00:25.480,0:00:29.240
Uya waiva musi wa January 22, 2011.

0:00:29.240,0:00:35.960
Mangwana acho pandakanga ndichidzokera, nenguva dza 4 zuva rovira ndakatanga kurwara zvakasimba;

0:00:35.960,0:00:40.980
Ndairutsa nekuita manyoka kwe maawa mashanu.

0:00:40.980,0:00:43.980
Ndakarutsa nzira yose kusvika ndasvika ku Bradford.

0:00:43.980,0:00:47.860
Panguva yandakazosvika ikoko, ndakanga ndapera simba zvakanyanya.

0:00:47.860,0:00:50.940
Ndakafunga kuti zvichida zvainge zvapera, kuti handichazorutsazve

0:00:50.940,0:00:52.600
uye kuti hapana chakaive chasara mumuviri wangu.

0:00:52.600,0:00:57.600
Zvadaro pandakaenda kumba kunorara pasi, kurutsa kutsva kwakatanga

0:00:57.600,0:01:01.660
Panguva ino ndakanzwa sokuti matumbo angu akanga achibuda mumuviri wangu

0:01:01.660,0:01:03.240
uye ini ndakanga ndisingazivi zvokuita.

0:01:03.240,0:01:08.940
Dzakange dzave 12 pakati pousiku, saka ndakadana vana vangu kuti vandiunzire kopuyuta yangu.

0:01:08.940,0:01:14.620
Ndaiziva kuti ndainge ndave kufa asi ndakafunga kuti dai ndangogona kutendera mumwe munhu kuti andinamatire.

0:01:14.620,0:01:17.680
Saka, ndakavaudza kuti vawane 'kuporeswa kwechi Kristu'.

0:01:17.680,0:01:22.900
Apo vakatsvaga pa YouTube, chiso chemu Porofita T.B. Joshua chakaonekwa.

0:01:22.900,0:01:26.560
Akabva atanga kunyengetera; akanyengetera zvakasimba kwazvo.

0:01:26.560,0:01:30.340
Paainyengetera, muviri wangu wakatanga kudedera.

0:01:30.340,0:01:35.040
Ipapo akati, "Bata sikirini ". Saka ndakabata sikirini,

0:01:35.040,0:01:38.040
uye muviri wangu waita sebenzi mumubhedha.

0:01:38.040,0:01:40.040
Zvino shure kweizvozvo ...

0:01:46.220,0:01:50.980
Ndaiziva kuti ndaisagona kusvika kuchipatara nekuti pakanga pasina nguva yakakwana;

0:01:50.980,0:01:55.620
Ndaiziva kuti ndakanga ndiri kufa uye iyi ndiyo chete nzira yandaive nayo kuti ndirarame.

0:01:55.620,0:01:59.080
Mwari akanga achitaura neni kuti ndaifanira kunamatirwa.

0:01:59.080,0:02:03.640
Apo muporofita akanga achindinyengeterera, ini ndakanga ndisingazivi kuti munhu uyu ndiani.

0:02:03.640,0:02:05.440
Akanga achingonyengetera zvakasimba.

0:02:05.440,0:02:09.340
Shure kwaizvozvo, akati kwandiri, "Simuka!"

0:02:09.340,0:02:11.340
Akaudza vanhu vose kuti 'Simuka!'.

0:02:11.340,0:02:16.380
Saka, ndakabva pamubhedha wangu ndokubva ndanzwa simba richiuya mukati momuviri wangu

0:02:16.380,0:02:20.200
uye mhondi huru kana chero chinhu ichocho, chichindisiya.

0:02:20.200,0:02:24.280
Ndakashamisika nokuti ndakanga ndarara pamubhedha nguva yose iyi, ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kupfakanyika

0:02:24.280,0:02:28.620
asi zvino kuburikidza neIndaneti, muPorofita T.B. Joshua aindiudza

0:02:28.620,0:02:30.200
kuti ndibve pamubhedha, achiti 'Simuka'.

0:02:30.200,0:02:33.840
Saka, ndakasimuka, ndakaenda kuchigezero ndokutarisa chiso changu.

0:02:33.840,0:02:37.240
Ndakanga ndarasikirwa nehuremu zvakanyanya kubva mumuviri wangu.

0:02:37.240,0:02:41.500
Ndakatarisa pachiso changu uye ndakaona chiso changu chiita se marangwanda.

0:02:41.500,0:02:47.880
Ini ndakazoziva kuti mamiriro aya epakati pekurarama kana kufa akange ari nekuda kwe nyasha dza Mwari ...

0:02:54.540,0:02:57.920
Nokuda kwe munhu wa Mwari uyu, ndiri mupenyu nhasi.

0:02:57.920,0:03:00.520
Handina kumbomuona kare muupenyu hwangu.

0:03:00.520,0:03:07.220
Zuva rakatevera, ndakatora vana vangu kuti vatsvage kuti ndiyani, kwaanobva, chechi yake ndeyipi.

0:03:07.220,0:03:10.000
Vakaona kuti ari ku Nigeria.

0:03:10.000,0:03:14.240
Saka ndakafunga, "Ndinoda kuenda kunomutenda asi....".

0:03:14.240,0:03:17.240
Ndinotenda Mwari nekuda kwa izvozvo.

0:03:17.240,0:03:24.780
Ndine chikwereti kuna Mwari kuna Jesu neku mu Porofita T.B. Joshua nokuti ndiri mupenyu nhasi.

0:03:24.780,0:03:29.600
Iropafadzo huru.

0:03:33.580,0:03:40.780
Manzwa kuna izvozvo here?

0:03:40.780,0:03:44.420
Kuburikidza ne YouTube.

0:03:44.420,0:03:46.300
Saizvozvo.

0:03:46.300,0:03:50.240
Haana kumboziva kuti izvi zvaibva ku Nigeria.

0:03:50.240,0:03:52.540
Asi mushure memunyengetero, mhinduro yakauya,

0:03:52.540,0:03:54.680
uye iye akabva ati, "Regai nditsvage (chechi iyi)".

0:03:54.680,0:04:00.160
Ndizvo zvose - YouTube!

0:04:00.160,0:04:02.800
Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari!

0:04:02.800,0:04:04.540
Saka, ndinokutendai.

0:04:04.540,0:04:10.540
Tinovimba kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

0:04:10.540,0:04:16.980
Dzvanya apa kuti unyorese kupupurira zvakawanda pamusoro pesimba ra Mwari pabasa munguva yatiri nhasi

0:04:16.980,0:04:21.340
kuti ugare uri pamusoro pezvichagoburwa zvehuporofita, dzikinuro,

0:04:21.340,0:04:26.160
mharidzo nezvapupu zvinobva ku Synagogue Church Of All Nations

